text: Hayley Carter and Ena Shibahara were the defending champions, but chose not to participate. Robin Anderson and Jessika Ponchet won the title, defeating Ann Li and Jamie Loeb in the final, 7–6(7–4), 6–7(5–7), [10–7]. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== *Main Draw Kentucky Bank Tennis Championships - Doubles Category:Lexington Challenger
